{"serial": "21034", "department_serial": 20, "code": "MA3123", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Topics in Financial Mathematics I", "ch": "金融數學專題Ⅰ"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen, Ting-Fu"], "ch": ["陳亭甫"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["7"]}, "loc": {"building": "M", "room": "218"}}, {"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "M", "room": "218"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "數學系", "en": "Department of Mathematics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 19, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "學生有能力可以進行數學建模、金融商品評價、模擬驗證以及風險管理的完整分析。同時具有能夠撰寫投資策略的程式以及進行回溯測試的能力。", "en": "Students are expected to be capable of financial derivative analysis, including mathematical modeling, derivatives pricing, simulation verification, and risk management. Besides, students are expected to be able to design the program for investment strategies and backtesting in the financial market."}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程主題可分為兩個方向。第一個是延續金融數學導論，學習如何利用進階的數學模型對金融衍生性商品進行定價、如何模擬各種模型下的資產價格以及如何利用價格的隱含資訊校準模型與解釋市場。第二個方向是金融市場的數據分析，首先撰寫不同的股市技術指標作為特徵，再設計投資策略，並透過回溯測試檢驗指標的投資績效，最後以機器學習方法進行訓練與預測。", "en": "The course contains two topics. The first one is to learn how to use advanced mathematical models to price financial derivatives, how to simulate asset prices under various models, and how to calibrate models and explain the market. The second topic is the data analysis of the financial market. First write different technical indicators as features, then design investment strategies, and check the investment performance through backtesting, and finally use machine learning methods to train and predict."}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. Steven E. Shreve, Stochastic Calculus for Finance II: Continuous-Time Models\n2. Python 金融分析（第二版）， Yves Hilpisch 著，賴屹民(譯)，歐萊禮出版社。", "en": "1. Steven E. Shreve, Stochastic Calculus for Finance II: Continuous-Time Models\n2. Python 金融分析（第二版）， Yves Hilpisch 著，賴屹民(譯)，歐萊禮出版社。"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中報告：30％\n期末專題：70％", "en": "Midterm Presentation:30％\nFinal Project:70％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三下午2-3點或另約時間。", "en": "Wed. 14:00-15:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "金融科技相關閱讀資料", "en": "FinTech related reading material"}, "domain": {"ch": "計算數學\n\n\n、\n\n\n機率統計", "en": "計算數學\n\n\n、\n\n\n機率統計"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "發掘問題", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯分析", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "演算能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "電腦應用", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "語文溝通", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "團隊合作", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "博雅通識", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "跨域整合", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Exploring problems", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Logical analysis", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Math skills", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Computer applications", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Communic